{"tid":567332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（慎入）好撚憎香港班憤世嫉俗班死毒撚，話緊你呀","createTime":"2018-02-20T18:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T09:48:24.000Z","uid":166313,"like":39,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e95bb7f3ab2c1c899cf7bc133196938fdd98e4cb","tid":567332,"uid":166313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:28:45.000Z","msg":"你毒都唔緊要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又要好撚有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到自己幾撚型幾撚威咁仲要成日做網絡判官:~屌鳩啲港女，（其實就係妒忌人）陏啲就話啲女人死臭雞死港女唔怪之得人哋想食洋腸都唔想食你地所謂嘅（20cm既司華力腸）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！屌你老母好心就死返屋企打飛機過世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你跟住一講公屋就一大班人死出黎喺度自我安慰打飛機吹奏到住公屋有幾撚好，矮化私樓價值其實就口裏說不心裏卻很誠實好撚想住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有呀，成撚日偷拍人上網跟住就打晒飛機咁起人哋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你哋係咪痴撚線㗎？人哋有乜撚嘢得罪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後講到自己月入幾撚多，個個都7 80k一個月又牛冿又哈佛咁撚樣，點解咁撚高學歷都係冇用都係一班垃圾一班沒家教既撚樣，最重要係咩？係你地成日覺得自己好撚清高，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要成日話自己米9中上樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果其實都係一班油頭4尺11既毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54457a28dd02520e095bc277fe2db6fd0724141e","tid":567332,"uid":166313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44edfe452aa45affe1c18de5ce3fbac28203085","tid":567332,"uid":166313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3e4a7534036ce64293f5d6819962a779528edc","tid":567332,"uid":166313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/